<root>

  <item>
    <name>Control_L+Shift_L to Fn (keep them pressed together to make Fn)</name>
    <identifier>private.control_shift_to_fn</identifier>
    <autogen>__KeyToKey__ KeyCode::CONTROL_L, ModifierFlag::SHIFT_L, KeyCode::FN</autogen>
    <autogen>__KeyToKey__ KeyCode::SHIFT_L, ModifierFlag::CONTROL_L, KeyCode::FN</autogen>
  </item>

  <item>
    <name>CapsLockOn+Control_L to Fn (toggle the Caps Lock on, then Control_L will become Fn; toggle it off, and Control_L will be Control again).</name>
    <identifier>private.capslock_control_to_fn</identifier>
    <block>
      ModifierFlag::CAPSLOCK,
    </block>
    <autogen>__KeyToKey__ KeyCode::CONTROL_L, KeyCode::FN</autogen>
  </item>

